.name
Ashido
.author
André Wichmann 
.version
1.0
.source
Includes source in assembly language.
.description
A clone of the commercial game 'Ishido'.  You must put 62 tiles with 6
different patterns and 6 different colors on a 12 x 7 board, but only tiles
with either same color or same pattern may touch each other.  Six different
game modes.  The best players scores are saved to disk.  
